- smoke A117: targeted cleanup (strip TESTVAULT* keys) instead of verbatim snapshot-restore — self-heals residue a botched run may have left (v...09's A117 fataled mid-plant before the require fix). Live box scrubbed of the TESTVAULT* leftovers. WP #736 follow-up.
