## 2026.05.07.01
- Bug 521 - autolaunch sweep now fires from server-side kill-off events. New AutoLaunchService::launchAllPending centralises the filter chain (autoLaunch flag, agent installed, not already running, resume rule). Triggers added: events/disks_mounted (array start), PLG INLINE (plugin upgrade), InitService one-shot boot marker. install-bg refactored from inline loop to service call. React mount trigger remains as defensive backstop. Smokes 72-76 added.
## 2026.05.06.22
- Bug 513 final - reorder _do_start so pidfile/flock claim happens BEFORE orphan reap. Without this, the InitService lazy backstop respawns a sibling supervisor mid-reap (whenever any Unraid AJAX poll lands during the 5s SIGKILL wait) and we mistake the new sibling for a stubborn orphan. Writing the pid up-front makes isRunning return true so concurrent ensureInit calls see us as the owner and skip start. Stubborn-orphan branch now logs and continues instead of refusing - we already hold the pidfile lock so we ARE the registered supervisor.
## 2026.05.06.21
- Smoke 48 reuses live supervisor instead of cycling. The PLG INLINE block always launches a supervisor right before publish-and-deploy runs the smoke, and InitService lazy-backstop respawns one whenever any Unraid WebGUI AJAX poll hits during the smoke window. Cycling supervisors mid-smoke triggers Bug 513 orphan reaper false positives. Now we just enqueue against whatever live supervisor exists.
## 2026.05.06.20
- Bug 513 follow-up - _do_start reaps orphans (TERM-wait-KILL) instead of refusing to start. Refusing only if a stubborn orphan survives SIGKILL. Smoke 70 updated. Without this, smoke 48 races the just-launched PLG-INLINE supervisor and the new supervisor refuses to start during smoke.
## 2026.05.06.19
- Smoke 48 prologue: path-anchored pgrep orphan sweep with 8s SIGTERM wait + SIGKILL fallback, matching cleanup.sh and PLG INLINE. Without this, smoke 48 race-launches a second supervisor before the prior one has died and trips the new Bug 513 orphan-detection bail.
## 2026.05.06.18
- Bug 512 plus 513 - install upgrade no longer triggers consolidation; supervisor handles it on schedule via the post-bake threshold trigger. Removed the D-332 sync consolidate from InstallerService and the post-install consolidate enqueue from install-bg. Retired consolidate_after_agent_install config key. Bug 513 orphan supervisor reaper added to cleanup.sh and _do_start and PLG INLINE - pgrep-based path-anchored sweep catches supervisors whose pidfile was clobbered by sibling stops. Smoke 67-71 added.
