- Robustified migrate_legacy
- sh to handle multiple potential storage locations and active mounts.
- Improved error reporting for missing mksquashfs during migration.
## 2026.04.10.14
- Fix: Refine logging levels and improve milestone visibility.
- Standardized milestone events (Start/Stop session, Install/Uninstall, Bake/Consolidate, Migration) to INFO level.
- Redirected all routine AJAX status polls and internal checks to DEBUG level to eliminate console flood.
- Updated all storage shell scripts to log critical milestones directly to the main debug log.
- Added explicit 'Migration not required' logging for systems already on the new architecture.
- Added detailed INFO level request tracing for user-initiated actions.
## 2026.04.10.13
- Fix: Restore agent discovery and activity logging.
- Refactored StorageMetricsService to scan the persistence path for all
- sqsh files, ensuring offline agents show up in the UI.
- Improved version retrieval to always read fresh from disk.
- Added explicit atomic locking for initialization to ensure exactly one INFO log per session.
- Restored INFO level request tracing for critical AJAX actions.
- Enhanced storage mounting feedback in the debug console.
## 2026.04.10.12
- Fix: Standardize unmounting and version retrieval.
