- sh to aggressively unmount all agent/home stacks during update.
- Disabled static version caching in ConfigService to ensure accurate version reporting.
- Added INFO level feedback when a mount operation is skipped because it is already active.
## 2026.04.10.11
- Fix: Restore logging visibility and resolve double-initialization.
