- Added INFO level request tracing in AICliAjax for critical actions (Start, Install, Stop).
- Enabled full output logging for storage mount shell scripts on failure.
- Added request deferral logging when storage migration is blocking initialization.
## 2026.04.10.10
- Fix: Implement first-run logging for plugin initialization.
- Added a persistent marker file in /tmp to ensure 'Initializing Plugin' is logged only once per reboot or update at INFO level.
- Subsequent requests remain at DEBUG level to avoid log flooding.
