## 2026.04.10.01
- Feat: Migrate storage architecture to ZRAM + OverlayFS + SquashFS.
- Replaced monolithic Btrfs img loop mounts with isolated high-performance SquashFS stacks.
- Implemented a single 4GB zstd-compressed ZRAM shared upper layer for all agents and user homes.
- Added background migration engine for seamless conversion of legacy Btrfs images to SquashFS.
- Implemented automatic volume splitting (3.9GB FAT32 threshold) for future-proofing.
- Updated StorageMountService, StorageMetricsService, and StorageMigrationService for SquashFS.
- Refactored UI 'System Resources' card to reflect the new architecture and added consolidation controls.
- Added migration status reporting and blocking overlay to prevent UI race conditions.

